{"tid":1511381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《 跳閘救港》唔敢跳閘嘅人，可以...","createTime":"2019-08-27T13:49:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T08:50:47.000Z","uid":40287,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f25ec301a7e9a38e0ff743a803c50f2f5335daef","tid":1511381,"uid":40287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:49:24.000Z","msg":"有好多人仲係衝破唔到嗰枷鎖，唔敢跳閘，唔敢捐過去，淆嘅人，可以點做？<br />\n<br />\n答案就係，盡量唔好搭火車，改搭其他交通工具，罷搭，你唔夠膽跳入去，就只有呢嗰方法，都做唔到嘅，算鳩數啦。"},{"pid":"7c543bc1ef692cd70c3f3804743f522c684e425c","tid":1511381,"uid":148082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:12:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/udfrCFg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FudfrCFg.jpg&h=9632946e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v3JwOMX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv3JwOMX.jpg&h=36428525&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"014ef8136606cef4d10cf3ab0791ed8c067b4f20","tid":1511381,"uid":40287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:21:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mpvrCJp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmpvrCJp.png&h=56a854bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"deaabb8dd3fa81f5ea656d4bae421a8db81c6a07","tid":1511381,"uid":73853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:26:53.000Z","msg":"未見過人跳閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9cbf1430c8f28a0db95154cc075c984e5f94c1","tid":1511381,"uid":40287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"deaabb8dd3fa81f5ea656d4bae421a8db81c6a07","tid":1511381,"uid":73853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:26:53.000Z","msg":"未見過人跳閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:35:31.000Z","msg":"聽朝如果你搭，抽小小時間，觀察十五分鐘。跳嘅人非常非常少，好多人知道有呢個呼籲存在，但因為各種原因唔敢做，既然唔敢做，就唔好搭佢，唔好畀錢佢賺，兩蚊都唔好畀佢，